foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: The difference between the number of requests pending at the end of FY2013 and the number pending at the beginning of FY2014 is attributable to components updating data or delaying their entry of closure data until after the EEOC report for FY2013 was generated. (EEOC generates the report data in October and November.) When a component fails to close a request or enter a new request in our FOIA Tracking System in a timely manner, the overall pending numbers will change. FY2014 numbers are the correct numbers.
